metadata.description: Caprice A.I. Diamond Club Pass gives you unique benefits within the Caprice A.I. ecosystem. By being one of only one hundred Diamond Club members, you own 0.2% of Caprice A.I. and are included in our monthly profit sharing program. You are also given priority lifetime access to all utility releases as well as free access to Caprice-powered adult establishments in future Metaverse integrations. As icing on the cake, your Diamond Club NFT gives you access to exclusive 1-on-1 lifestyle coaching.
metadata.name: Caprice A.I. Diamond Club
